{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Welcome to <strong>Grimlord</strong> - a <strong>Dark Fantasy Action Souls-like RPG</strong> built on <strong>Unreal Engine 5</strong> for VR. Awakened in a monastery deep in the Lonely Mountains, you walk in an epic quest as the adventurer standing before the darkness and striving for the light against the tyrannical Grim Lord.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/extras/creative-min.png?t=1735234393\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/extras/\u5206\u9875\u67612.png?t=1735234393\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/extras/boss_1.gif?t=1735234393\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You\u2019re a prisoner in a monastery somewhere deep in the Lonely Mountains. You are free to choose how to fight your way out. Choose your way of becoming a battling adventurer whilst standing before the darkness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/extras/\u5206\u9875\u67612.png?t=1735234393\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/extras/dynamic_combat.gif?t=1735234393\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Grimlord brings combat in VR like never before. With a ton of unique enemies sprawling the monastery grounds capable of showing you their individual combat prowess, you\u2019re left to learn how to deal with them efficiently - for survival\u2019s sake.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/extras/\u5206\u9875\u67612.png?t=1735234393\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/extras/\u4eba\u5f62.gif?t=1735234393\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Are you a battle-hardened sword &amp; shield adventurer or a staff-wielding magic artist? Maybe a long-ranged bow &amp; arrow assassin? How about an agile dual-wielding bladesman? Even go wild as a shield &amp; dagger throwing specialist? The choice is yours, prisoner.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/extras/\u5206\u9875\u67612.png?t=1735234393\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/extras/weapons.gif?t=1735234393\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/extras/weapon_talents.gif?t=1735234393\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With boss battles meant to test your accumulated skills and knowledge, each encounter assures every prisoner\u2019s adventure to strive for the light is as unique as it can be.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1735234393","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/page.bg.jpg?t=1735234393","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/f3e207059ada5abc6876effa38a975aedd0b2f6a/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1735234393","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/f3e207059ada5abc6876effa38a975aedd0b2f6a/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1735234393","categories":[{"description":"Singl