extras/dynamic_combat.gif?t=1735234393\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Grimlord brings combat in VR like never before. With a ton of unique enemies sprawling the monastery grounds capable of showing you their individual combat prowess, you\u2019re left to learn how to deal with them efficiently - for survival\u2019s sake.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/extras/\u5206\u9875\u67612.png?t=1735234393\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/extras/\u4eba\u5f62.gif?t=1735234393\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Are you a battle-hardened sword &amp; shield adventurer or a staff-wielding magic artist? Maybe a long-ranged bow &amp; arrow assassin? How about an agile dual-wielding bladesman? Even go wild as a shield &amp; dagger throwing specialist? The choice is yours, prisoner.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/extras/\u5206\u9875\u67612.png?t=1735234393\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/extras/weapons.gif?t=1735234393\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/extras/weapon_talents.gif?t=1735234393\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With boss battles meant to test your accumulated skills and knowledge, each encounter assures every prisoner\u2019s adventure to strive for the light is as unique as it can be.</p>","developers":["Metalcat Interactive Co.,Ltd"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"},